This paper deals with photorealistic style transfer, which is a technique commonly used in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning and optimization techniques, which are common in machine learning (cs.MM - Machine Learning) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI - Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with graphics and visualizations, which are covered in cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Finally, the paper uses optimization techniques, which are also covered in cs.LG (Machine Learning).
